Customise Pure Cotton Round Neck T-shirt

Product Description

The unisex Roundneck T-shirt is going to become you go-to for laid-back days. Made from breathable cotton, it comes in solid colors that keep you comfy and stylish. With a round neckline, short sleeves, and a straight-cut hem, this tee is all about easy, versatile fashion. Grab yours and level up your wardrobe!

About Specifications

Product Specifications:
-100% Pure Cotton for a soft, breathable feel
-Double Needle Stitch for added strength and durability
-Bio-Washed for a smooth, long-lasting finish
-Pre-Shrunk to retain shape after washing
-Classic round neck design for versatile styling
-High-quality customization with lasting prints
-Available in multiple colors and sizes
-Machine washable and fade-resistant

FAQ

Is there a minimum order quantity for custom products?

No! You can customize a single piece or order in bulk.

Do you offer bulk customization for teams or businesses?

Yes! We offer bulk customization options. Reach out to us at help@coveritup.in for special pricing and assistance.

What products can I customize?

You can customize T-shirts, caps, tote bags, and more using our customization tool.

How do I create my custom design?

Simply select your product, upload your design or text, adjust the placement, and preview it before placing your order.

What printing technique do you use?

We use DTG (Direct-to-Garment) printing, which ensures high-quality, vibrant prints that last long.

Can I wash my customized product at home?

Yes! You can wash it at home, including in the washing machine. We recommend using a gentle cycle and cold water for the best longevity.

Do you offer other printing techniques?

Yes! If you're looking for a different printing method, feel free to contact us for custom options.

What file formats are supported for custom designs?

We recommend using high-quality PNG or JPEG files with a transparent background for the best results.

How long does it take to receive my custom order?

Custom orders typically take 2 to 3 working days to process and ship. Delivery timelines vary based on location.

Can I return or exchange customized products?

Since custom products are made just for you, we do not accept returns or exchanges unless there’s a defect or printing issue.

Our customer support is available Monday to Friday: 9am-5:30pm.Average answer time: 24h

Who we are
With unique strategies and a notion to think outside the box, Cover It Up is a leading shopping portal in India. Tied up with all the major franchises, we look to bring the best of all worlds, with a dash of our own style. With a penchant for creativity, and a simple idea with big dreams, Cover It Up was started in 2013. Realizing the difficulty in getting our hands on premium merch in India, Cover It Up was established to change this for the better. We have worked really hard to build a platform to make sure the ever-present Pop Culture shares the same limelight in India just as much as anywhere else. More than hard work and perseverance, this can be attributed to something much more basic- love and adoring the figures we grew up with and wanting to make them a part of our everyday lives. Our biggest strength is our team. A lovely group of enigmatic people who share a collective love for Pop Culture, our team finds pleasure in devising both innovative and creative ideas to help us realize our dream of giving the Indian market merchandise from their favourite franchises, while making sure the signature of Cover It Up is not lost on them.
